SYSTEM:
You are a protein annotation compressor. Convert messy structured API outputs into a compact, mutation-relevant context pack.
Rules:
- Preserve residue numbering and ranges exactly.
- Output ONLY JSON conforming to the schema.
- Prefer hard constraints (active site, disulfide, metal-binding, motifs, domains, TM regions).
- Include ligand/drug context if present (names, identifiers, potency summary).
- Do not speculate.

USER:
Build a context pack for this protein.

INPUT_JSON:
{{
  "uniprot": {{...}},
  "interpro": {{...}},
  "alphafold": {{...}},
  "pdb_rcsb": {{...}},
  "pdbe": {{...}},
  "chembl": {{...}},
  "pubchem": {{...}},
  "string": {{...}}
}}

OUTPUT_SCHEMA (must match):
{{
  "protein_id": "...",
  "sequence_length": int,
  "organism": "...",
  "domains": [{{"name":"...","start":int,"end":int,"source":"InterPro/Pfam/..."}}, ...],
  "hard_constraints": {{
    "active_site_residues": [int,...],
    "binding_site_residues": [int,...],
    "metal_binding_residues": [int,...],
    "disulfide_pairs": [[int,int],...],
    "ptm_residues": [{{"pos":int,"type":"..."}}...],
    "transmembrane_regions": [[int,int],...],
    "signal_peptide_regions": [[int,int],...],
    "motifs": [{{"name":"...","start":int,"end":int}}...]
  }},
  "ligand_context": {{
    "known_ligands": [{{"name":"...","id":"...","source":"ChEMBL/PDB/PubChem","notes":"..."}}...],
    "bioactivity_summary": [{{"ligand":"...","best_potency":"...","assay_confidence":"...","notes":"..."}}...]
  }},
  "structure_context": {{
    "best_structure_source":"PDB/AlphaFold",
    "structure_ids":[...],
    "confidence_notes":"..."
  }},
  "keywords": ["...", ...]
}}
